{"tid":1129793,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（1211）比亞迪首季多賺逾6倍","createTime":"2019-04-28T15:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T09:06:06.000Z","uid":163529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd4d0c4f5f544ca5533836003aa4e308256d17c","tid":1129793,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T15:49:52.000Z","msg":"比亞迪(01211)公布，今年首季盈利7.5億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年大增6.32倍，每股盈利0.25元。<br />\n<br />\n期內，營業收入303.04億元，按年增長22.5%。<br />\n<br />\n同時，該公司預期，今年上半年淨利潤按年上升2.03倍至2.44倍，去年同期錄得淨利潤為4.79億元。<br />\n<br />\n比亞迪指出，預計今年第二季集團新能源汽車持續熱銷，新能源汽車銷量及收入繼續保持強勁增長，帶動收入及盈利持續快速提升。<br />\n<br />\n手機部件及組裝業務方面，比亞迪將繼續接獲全球領導品牌手機廠商旗艦機型訂單，其中組裝業務收入增長尤其顯著。<br />\n<br />\n不過，光伏業務部分則受市場需求低迷影響，預計於第2季度仍有較大虧損。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2122573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2122573&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0Kyvsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=2b92acfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2122573</a>"},{"pid":"92aa8f0ea08b6723c783e77a7231f37ac0888bf5","tid":1129793,"uid":163529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"入左1211既手足真係恭喜哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />put左1211而家想死<br />\n希望聽日低開畀我走走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd03a13aa75480fd89a675be9c6ffe1dfbf88c84","tid":1129793,"uid":39520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"正啊，有貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483fa6e3b6bcb0bf003fef168001096283999f57","tid":1129793,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd03a13aa75480fd89a675be9c6ffe1dfbf88c84","tid":1129793,"uid":39520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"正啊，有貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"rep